<div class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content">
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <p>If you haven't yet already, we highly recommend checking out the <a class="link" href="/">NeverFap Deluxe Homepage</a>.</p>
      <p>It explores in great detail what you can expect from NeverFap Deluxe, as well as an introduction into some of the skills you'll be learning from the materials on this website.</p>
      <p>We then recommend checking out the <a class="link" href="/guide">NeverFap Deluxe Guide</a> which follows on from the homepage, and provides additional knowledge and context.</p>
      <p>From there you can check out the various articles and practices which have been designed to help you better understand yourself, as well provide you with tangible exercises you can do on a daily basis.</p>
      <p>Only you have the power to do this.</p>
      <p>Certainly, I want to help you, but only if you're willing to put one foot forward in front of the other.</p>
      <p>Do you wanna play ball?</p>
    </div>
  </div>


